Tools for i3 window manager.

Installation
------------

.. code-block:: text

   pip install i3tools

Usage
-----

i3ws
~~~~

Go to previous/next workspace.

.. code-block:: text

   i3ws <prev|next>

Configuration:

.. code-block:: text

   bindsym $mod+Ctrl+Left exec i3ws prev
   bindsym $mod+Ctrl+Right exec i3ws next
